                "invention-title": [
                    "Novel low-carbon vertical integrated secondary reduction iron furnace",
                    "新型低碳竖立一体式二次还原铁炉"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a novel low-carbon vertical integrated secondary reduction iron furnace, and relates to the technical field of reduction iron furnaces, the novel low-carbon vertical integrated secondary reduction iron furnace comprises a first reduction bin, a second reduction bin and a cooling protection bin, the first reduction bin, the second reduction bin and the cooling protection bin are cylindrical, the first reduction bin is located at the top end of the second reduction bin, and the second reduction bin is located at the bottom end of the cooling protection bin. The second reduction bin is located above the cooling protection bin, and a feeding drying bin is installed at the top end of the first reduction bin. According to the method, the reduction time is short, the hydrogen is the strongest and environment-friendly reducing agent and rapidly generates chemical action with the fine iron powder in the reduction process, the metal reduction effect is completed, and the general reduction time is 45-60 minutes; hydrogen reduction and emission are H20, and the method is the most environment-friendly reduction scheme; primary reduction and secondary reduction are integrally carried out, so that the time and energy for repeatedly heating and cooling are saved; the novel furnace is simple in installation infrastructure, easy to operate, low in investment, adjustable in furnace capacity according to actual requirements and suitable for being used in mine fields of various sizes."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了新型低碳竖立一体式二次还原铁炉，涉及还原铁炉技术领域，包括第一还原仓、第二还原仓和冷却保护仓，所述第一还原仓、所述第二还原仓和所述冷却保护仓呈圆柱型设计，所述第一还原仓位于所述第二还原仓的顶端，所述第二还原仓位于所述冷却保护仓的上方，所述第一还原仓的顶端安装有进料干燥仓。本发明还原时间短，氢气是最强和环保的还原剂，在还原过程中迅速与铁精粉产生化学作用，完成金属还原效果，一般还原时间在45‑60分鈡；氢气还原，排放是H20，是最环保的还原方案；一、二次还原一体式进行，省却重复升温降温的时间和能枆；新型炉安装基建简单，操作容易，投资少，炉容量可按实际需要调整，适合各大小矿场使用。"
                }
            ]
